cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with crosslingual word representations and document classification tasks. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel neural network architecture. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves natural language processing and semantic understanding. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with document classification, and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves the use of neural networks for representation learning.
